      "heading": null,
      "description": "Make the Roast Chicken with Schmaltzy Courgettes."
    },
    {
      "heading": null,
      "description": "Bring the chicken stock to the boil in a large saucepan. Add the rice and cook, stirring, for 10-12 mins until soft."
    },
    {
      "heading": null,
      "description": "Meanwhile, shred the leftover chicken and finely chop the dill and parsley."
    },
    {
      "heading": null,
      "description": "Once the rice is cooked, stir in the chicken and courgettes. Simmer for another 2-3 mins until everything is piping hot."
    },
    {
      "heading": null,
      "description": "Squeeze in as much lemon juice as you like, then stir through the chopped herbs. Taste and season with salt and black pepper."
    },
    {
      "heading": null,
      "description": "Ladle into bowls, drizzle over a little olive oil and serve with a wedge of lemon."
